Got Junk in your trunk?

descriptionHtml:
Are you tired of Walking around with so much trash in your inventory???
Well say no more!
With DOVAHBOX!!!!
Well Its a junkbox... You can store junk in there that you dont need...

This isn\'t a special mod, but It can be useful for you.

The junkbox comes with free gold and instructions on how to use it, blah blah...
You can find it at Alvor\'s Forge at riverwood

Enjoy! and clean yo shiz!
